data.description: Great cabin close to the Mt. Fork River! This property would be perfect for anyone looking for a place to get away and enjoy a little bit of seclusion. It is currently being enjoyed by the owner but could easily become a rental property. Beautiful pine trees surround the cabin and add to the seclusion. With easy access to the river and Broken Bow, this location makes it convenient for a new owner to enjoy their favorite outdoor activities and be close to town at the same time. Call to schedule your private showing today!
